Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.90,0:01:35.60,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不管夜晚还是白天,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.01,0:01:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nighttime or daytime,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.77,0:01:39.46,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,一旦你踏进了这个地方,\N你就分不出日夜了.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.88,0:01:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once you get a few feet into this place,\Nyou can't tell the difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.64,0:01:43.20,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,或许这就是为什么它能\N保持着原生态.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.75,0:01:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably why it's all remained\Nso untouched.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.38,0:01:45.81,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,先生们，一步一小心.\N提高警觉.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.52,0:01:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One step at a time, gentlemen.\NKeep your eyes peeled.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.03,0:01:48.90,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,来走这边, 在你的右边, 库.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.15,0:01:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over this way, to your right, Coop.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.90,0:01:52.07,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哈里,\N有人已经来过这儿了.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.02,0:01:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harry,\Nsomeone's been here already.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.25,0:01:54.81,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,瞧, 他们做了本该我们做的事.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.36,0:01:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, they did our work for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.99,0:01:57.29,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,噢, 我的上帝.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.10,0:01:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.33,0:02:05.46,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我在发电站外面\N看到了一样的鞋印.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.47,0:02:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l saw the same tracks\Noutside the power station.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.81,0:02:11.25,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,重心在左脚.\N前掌与脚跟之间有空隙.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.94,0:02:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weight shift to the left foot.\NA break in the heel.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.42,0:02:13.20,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,云顿·厄尔.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.55,0:02:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Windom Earle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.38,0:02:15.25,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,厄尔来这干什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.48,0:02:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What would Earle be doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.42,0:02:19.07,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那可是一个让人毛骨悚然\N又值得深思的问题.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.55,0:02:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a frightening question\Nto contemplate.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.12,0:02:22.42,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,安迪, 我需要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.22,0:02:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Andy, l'm gonna need
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.60,0:02:25.64,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,一幅这个岩石雕刻的\N大幅精确素描图.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.72,0:02:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,an accurate large-scale\Nrendering of this petroglyph.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.81,0:02:28.38,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哈里, 我们要给布里格斯少校\N打电话.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.93,0:02:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harry, let's get Major Briggs\Non the horn.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.60,0:02:30.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你想他到警局\N和我们见面吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.70,0:02:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want him to meet us\Nat the station?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.29,0:02:32.07,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,对.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.40,0:02:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the ticket.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.72,0:02:50.29,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,从前,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.85,0:02:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once upon a time,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.46,0:02:54.51,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,有一个至高无上的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.58,0:02:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there was a place of great goodness
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.68,0:02:57.51,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,叫守日门.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.82,0:02:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,called the White Lodge.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.68,0:03:02.81,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,温顺的小鹿在那儿嬉戏\N沉浸在快乐之中, 到处欢声笑语.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.79,0:03:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gentle fawns gamboled there\Namidst happy, laughing spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.99,0:03:07.03,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,空气中瀰漫着天真无邪\N和欣喜的气息.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.10,0:03:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sounds of innocence and joy\Nfilled the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.20,0:03:12.68,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,雨露, 是甘露美酒\N滋润着人们的心灵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.33,0:03:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And when it rained, it rained\Nsweet nectar that infused one's heart
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.86,0:03:18.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,滋润着人们在生活中\N渴望的真理和美丽.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.97,0:03:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with a desire to live life\Nin truth and beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.07,0:03:24.55,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,总的来说, 真是一个惨白恐怖的地方,\N到处充斥着贞节的酸臭味.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.18,0:03:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Generally speaking, a ghastly place,\Nreeking of virtue's sour smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.72,0:03:26.51,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,到处都塞满了\N那些呢喃的祷告者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.85,0:03:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Engorged with\Nthe whispered prayers
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.68,0:03:29.85,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那些虔诚跪拜的母亲,\N呀呀啼哭的初生儿,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.82,0:03:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of kneeling mothers,\Nmewling newborns,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.03,0:03:35.03,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,还有傻子, 老老少少,\N毫无理由的被强迫着去做好事.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.16,0:03:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and fools, young and old,\Ncompelled to do good without reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.72,0:03:38.72,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但我很高兴的指出\N我们的故事还没完结
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.86,0:03:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But l am happy to point out\Nthat our story does not end
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.90,0:03:42.25,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,在这个过度肉麻又卑鄙的\N悲惨世界里.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.00,0:03:42.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in this wretched place\Nof saccharine excess.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.42,0:03:46.25,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,原来还有另一个地方.\N恰恰相反.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.54,0:03:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For there's another place.\Nlts opposite.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.42,0:03:49.85,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那是一个几乎\N超乎想像力的地方,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.54,0:03:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A place of almost\Nunimaginable power,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.03,0:03:53.94,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,塞满了暗黑能量\N和恶毒秘密.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.14,0:03:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,chock-full of dark forces\Nand vicious secrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.16,0:03:58.55,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,没有祷告者敢进入\N这个吓人的无底洞.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.28,0:03:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No prayers dare enter\Nthis frightful maw.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.72,0:04:02.38,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,在那儿的亡灵才不关心什么\N善行或圣僧似的祈祷.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.85,0:04:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spirits there care not for good deeds\Nor priestly invocations.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.55,0:04:04.55,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他们会把你的肉\N从你的骨头上撕扯下来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.69,0:04:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are as like\Nto rip the flesh from your bone
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.72,0:04:07.11,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,作为欢迎你愉快一天的开始.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.86,0:04:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as greet you with a happy good day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.29,0:04:11.20,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,如果好好加以利用,\N那么，在这撕心裂肺，尖叫四起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.43,0:04:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if harnessed,\Nthese spirits in this hidden land
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.38,0:04:14.24,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,的地方里隐藏的\N亡灵们就会为
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.50,0:04:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of unmuffled screams\Nand broken hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.42,0:04:17.07,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,它们的新主人提供无边的法力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.53,0:04:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will offer up a power so vast
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.25,0:04:23.72,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好让他随心所欲的\N把世界玩弄于股掌之中.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.37,0:04:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that its bearer might reorder\Nthe earth itself to his liking.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.94,0:04:30.37,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我现在所讲的这个地方\N就被称作守夜门.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.04,0:04:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, this place l speak of\Nis known as the Black Lodge.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.55,0:04:33.24,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,而我决意要找到它.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.68,0:04:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And l intend to find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.94,0:04:35.42,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿, 伙计,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.05,0:04:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, man,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.59,0:04:37.33,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这故事很酷啊,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.72,0:04:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the story's cool,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.51,0:04:39.94,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但你答应过我有啤酒喝的.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.62,0:04:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you promised me beer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.11,0:04:42.07,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你还跟我说\N会有派对的啊.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.23,0:04:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You told me\Nthere was gonna be a party.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.24,0:04:48.50,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊, 什么破烂守日门守夜门?\N照我说, 有什么大不了的?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.36,0:04:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l mean, White Lodge, Black Lodge?\Nl mean, what's the big deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.72,0:04:54.72,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,时间刚好, 年轻人.\N万事有道.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.84,0:04:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ln time, young man.\NEverything in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.16,0:05:25.64,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我想我再也不会见到第二个\N如乔西般可爱的女孩了.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.30,0:05:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l think that l shall never see\Na girl as lovely as Josie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.37,0:05:29.46,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,当她走进房间,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.51,0:05:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When she walks into a room,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.64,0:05:33.81,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,花儿也为之敬礼,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.78,0:05:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the flowers all stood up,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.51,0:05:37.29,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,人去楼空,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.65,0:05:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to room,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.07,0:05:40.33,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,命啊,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.18,0:05:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,doom,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.51,0:05:44.77,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,如烟, 如梦...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.62,0:05:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,fume, gloom...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.72,0:05:51.07,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我想我再也不会见到第二个\N如乔西般可爱的女孩了.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.83,0:05:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l think that l shall never see\Na girl as lovely as Josie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.29,0:05:57.85,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,当她踏进房间,\N所有的花朵都要为之绽放.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.40,0:05:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When she walks into a room,\Nthe flowers were all abloom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.37,0:06:02.68,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 噢, 乔西.\N- 喂, 你的感伤还有完没完啊，快停止.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.51,0:06:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Oh, Josie.\N- Oh, stop your incessant moping.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.85,0:06:04.59,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,快来帮我看看这个该死的盒子.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.98,0:06:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a hand with this damn box.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.81,0:06:09.85,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你到底想我\N为你做什么呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.91,0:06:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What exactly\Nwould you like me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.37,0:06:13.90,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,打开它. 我已经试了好几天了.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.48,0:06:14.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Open it. l've been trying for days.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.07,0:06:16.33,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,托马斯·埃卡死的时候\N把这个留给我.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.19,0:06:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thomas Eckhardt\Nleft this to me when he died.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.50,0:06:19.90,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我要它打开,\N马上打开.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.62,0:06:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And l want it opened,\Nl want it opened now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.07,0:06:23.20,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那好, 让我们先来看看.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.19,0:06:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's have a look-see here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.37,0:06:24.72,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你有钥匙吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.50,0:06:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have a key?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.59,0:06:30.29,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你说呢? 如果我有钥匙的话,\N它早就打开了.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.70,0:06:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lf l had a key, it would be open,\Ndon't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.72,0:06:35.81,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯, 它连个钥匙孔\N都没有.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.84,0:06:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it doesn't even have\Na keyhole.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.07,0:06:40.55,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是一个暗箱.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.18,0:06:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's a puzzle box.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.72,0:06:45.72,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我以前在关岛的工艺品店\N见过一个类似的.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.85,0:06:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l saw one of these\Nat a crafts emporium on Guam.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.89,0:06:50.11,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我当时正和一对叫杜力图的双胞胎\N在那儿大肆挥霍.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.02,0:06:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l was there taking a little R and R\Nwith the Doolittle twins.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.37,0:06:52.37,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,荒唐的你简直\N不敢相信,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.49,0:06:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a monkey show\Nyou wouldn't believe,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.55,0:06:56.29,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那个戴尔·杜力图--\N就是, 他是2个里大的那个--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.66,0:06:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and Dale Doolittle--\NNow, he was the larger of the two--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.46,0:06:59.55,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,说到这，我想起来了, 就双胞胎来说,\N他们不算长得特别相像.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.60,0:06:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, for twins,\Nthey weren't all that much alike.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.72,0:07:01.85,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,彼得!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.87,0:07:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Peter!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.29,0:07:04.98,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思, 小松狮.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.40,0:07:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, poodle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.20,0:07:10.89,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这机关就是把其中一条配上对\N仅此而已.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.34,0:07:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The trick is to fit the pieces together\Njust so.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.07,0:07:13.59,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那要多久?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.18,0:07:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And how long will it take?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.11,0:07:19.15,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,难说, 可能几年.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.25,0:07:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this could take years.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.29,0:07:26.81,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,雪, 我已经对将来的事\N考虑了很多.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.42,0:07:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shel, l've been doing a lot of thinking\Nabout the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.98,0:07:30.11,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,以及怎么\N在这个世界混下去.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.13,0:07:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what it takes\Nto get ahead in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.29,0:07:34.59,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我读书看报, 看电视,\N忽然间，我灵光一闪:
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.43,0:07:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm reading up, watching TV,\Nsuddenly it hits me:
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.07,0:07:37.63,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,原来成功的秘诀就是.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.20,0:07:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The secret to success.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.46,0:07:41.68,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,只要人长得漂亮\N就可以呼风唤雨.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.57,0:07:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beautiful people\Nget everything they want.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.89,0:07:43.76,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 波比.\N- 真的, 想想看啊.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.01,0:07:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Bobby.\N- Yeah, think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.94,0:07:46.37,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你啥时见过\N一个金发美人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.04,0:07:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When's the last time you saw\Na beautiful blonde
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.50,0:07:49.07,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,会被判死刑的?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.65,0:07:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,go to the electric chair?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.76,0:07:53.76,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你就非常美丽, 雪莉.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.88,0:07:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are very beautiful, Shelly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.63,0:07:59.07,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我想是时候要好好利用\N我们的优势了，美人计.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.75,0:07:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And l think it's time we took advantage\Nof this beautiful people's conspiracy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.29,0:08:01.94,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那你认识哪个参议员能和我结婚吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.39,0:08:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Know any senators l can marry?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.55,0:08:04.02,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,先看看这个.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.66,0:08:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.46,0:08:07.28,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,双峰小姐.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.56,0:08:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Twin Peaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.46,0:08:11.15,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,一旦我们赢得了桂冠,\N宝贝, 天界无限啊.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.60,0:08:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once we get that crown on your head,\Nbaby, the sky is the limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.33,0:08:14.37,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,做梦, 波比,\N还有客人等着我的.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.44,0:08:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dream on, Bobby,\Nl have tables to wait on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.55,0:08:17.29,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,雪莉, 听着, 别和我争执了.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.67,0:08:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shelly, listen, don't argue with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.50,0:08:20.42,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,波比说了算,\N你懂了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.61,0:08:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bobby's in charge,\Nyou understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.46,0:08:24.33,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们今天下午\N一定要去报名.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.58,0:08:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to enlist\Nby this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.42,0:08:37.63,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,亲爱的，有件事\N我想要你为我做.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.56,0:08:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something\Nl want you to do for me, darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.02,0:08:43.63,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,只要身心能承受的\N我都会为你做.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.13,0:08:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'll do anything\Nthat body and mind can stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.20,0:08:48.15,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,难道这几天以来\N还不能证明么?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.34,0:08:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surely the last few days\Nhave been proof of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.50,0:08:52.50,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你尽管说吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.61,0:08:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just name it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.33,0:08:58.85,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我要赢\N双峰小姐比赛.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.45,0:08:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l wanna win\Nthe Miss Twin Peaks contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.02,0:09:00.81,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你就尽管说吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.15,0:09:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just name it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.02,0:09:06.54,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我要赢\N双峰小姐比赛.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.16,0:09:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l wanna win\Nthe Miss Twin Peaks contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.68,0:09:09.37,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哦, 这还用说吗.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.79,0:09:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.54,0:09:12.54,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯, 我以前做过一，两次\N颇有名气的演讲.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.66,0:09:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, l've been known\Nto make a speech or two in my time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.72,0:09:15.15,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我会连夜辅导你怎么作选美演讲.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.87,0:09:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'll coach you day and night.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.59,0:09:19.76,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,噢, 听着, 甜心.\N宝贝, 我不是这个意思.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.74,0:09:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, now, sweetheart.\NBaby, that's not what l'm talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.98,0:09:22.59,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,现在, 你是评委之一.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.11,0:09:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, you're one of the judges.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.76,0:09:24.50,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以左右结果的.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.91,0:09:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can guarantee it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.37,0:09:29.20,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但是-- 但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.48,0:09:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But-- But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.89,0:09:31.41,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那是错误的.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.02,0:09:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt would be wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.20,0:09:34.63,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那好, 听着, 亲爱的--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.32,0:09:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, now, darling--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.81,0:09:36.94,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,亲爱的, 那是爱的表现.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.92,0:09:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darling, it would be love.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.11,0:09:39.11,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,仅此而已.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.26,0:09:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.15,0:09:43.54,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道,\N我愿意为你做任何事, 拉娜.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.26,0:09:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know,\Nl'd do anything for you, Lana.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.72,0:09:46.28,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你是知道的.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.83,0:09:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.54,0:09:50.41,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是的, 爱人, 我知道.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.67,0:09:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, lover, l do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.07,0:10:01.93,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 早上好, 安妮.\N- 嗨. 吃早餐吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.18,0:10:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Good morning, Annie.\N- Hi. Breakfast?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.11,0:10:04.76,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我有4个如饥似渴的公安\N在外面的巡逻车上等着呢.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.25,0:10:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l've got four hungry lawmen\Nout in the police cruiser.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.93,0:10:07.80,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要甜甜圈和咖啡. 热的.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.08,0:10:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need donuts and coffee. Hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.02,0:10:10.37,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,2杯黑咖啡, 2杯白咖啡,\N不加糖, 麻烦你了.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.15,0:10:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two black, two white,\Nno sugars, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.89,0:10:13.63,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 马上来.\N- 噢, 还有，安妮?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.02,0:10:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Coming right up.\N- Oh, and Annie?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.94,0:10:16.67,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我想借这个机会\N邀请你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.06,0:10:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'd like to take this opportunity\Nto ask you
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.85,0:10:19.46,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,参加今天下午的业余自然研究\N不止你是否愿意伴我同行?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.96,0:10:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if you'd like to accompany me\Non a nature study this afternoon?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.98,0:10:22.98,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,自然研究?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.10,0:10:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nature study?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.20,0:10:24.93,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好啊.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.30,0:10:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.11,0:10:27.59,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那太棒了.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.24,0:10:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.15,0:10:29.54,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.27,0:10:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.33,0:10:32.15,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,每当我和你说话,\N我都既紧张又兴奋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.44,0:10:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When l talk to you,\Nl get a tingling sensation
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.33,0:10:34.24,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,从胃到脚趾头，浑身发抖.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.45,0:10:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in my toes and in my stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.93,0:10:36.28,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,有意思.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.05,0:10:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.85,0:10:39.20,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得\N跟喝了咖啡没太大关系.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.98,0:10:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l don't think\Nit has anything to do with coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.28,0:10:43.20,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我去拿甜甜圈.\N- 谢谢.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.42,0:10:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- l'll get those donuts.\N- Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.72,0:10:51.28,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,雪莉?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.83,0:10:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shelly?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.46,0:10:54.46,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你很美, 明白吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.60,0:10:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are beautiful, got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.59,0:10:56.98,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,把它用作你的优势.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.73,0:10:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Use it to your advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.93,0:11:01.63,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,"这世间一切的甜蜜之事价值何在,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.07,0:11:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,''What is all this sweet work worth,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.85,0:11:04.19,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,如果汝不吻我?"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.98,0:11:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if thou kiss not me?''
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.37,0:11:05.63,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你刚说什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.48,0:11:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l beg your pardon?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.85,0:11:10.72,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哦, 是一首无名诗\N也不知谁送来的.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.98,0:11:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it was an anonymous poem\Nsomeone sent me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.89,0:11:12.54,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,雪莉,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.02,0:11:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shelly,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.72,0:11:14.63,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我需要立即看这首诗.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.85,0:11:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l need to see this poem immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.72,0:11:17.46,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好的.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.86,0:11:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.11,0:11:21.85,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,它被分成3部分,\N我们每个人有一部分.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.23,0:11:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt was in three pieces,\Nwe each got a piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.98,0:11:24.50,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 唐娜, 欧蕊和我.\N- 谢谢你.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.13,0:11:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Donna, Audrey and me.\N- Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.72,0:11:32.32,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这个我要留着.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.84,0:11:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l need to keep this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.33,0:11:35.63,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 好.\N- 谢谢你.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.44,0:11:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Okay.\N- Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.02,0:11:40.32,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,一打甜甜圈, 4杯咖啡,\N2黑, 2白, 无糖.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.14,0:11:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A dozen donuts, four cups of coffee,\Ntwo black, two white, no sugar.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.85,0:11:42.19,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.98,0:11:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.37,0:11:45.24,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 库珀探员?\N- 是.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.52,0:11:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Agent Cooper?\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.80,0:11:48.24,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,今天下午?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.95,0:11:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This afternoon?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.85,0:11:52.41,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我会来这儿找你.\N四点整.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.99,0:11:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'll meet you right here.\NFour o'clock sharp.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.50,0:12:07.89,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,"山之吻.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.64,0:12:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,''Mountains kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.06,0:12:10.45,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,波延绵.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.17,0:12:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Waves clasp.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.63,0:12:12.93,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,花儿..."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.78,0:12:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Flower...''
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.15,0:12:15.24,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这都什么玩意儿啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.28,0:12:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.89,0:12:19.06,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是一首诗, 哈里. 被撕成3份.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.02,0:12:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's a poem, Harry. Torn into thirds.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.24,0:12:23.71,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,分别送到了雪莉·强生, 欧蕊·荷恩\N和唐娜·海沃德那里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.35,0:12:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sent to Shelly Johnson, Audrey Horne\Nand Donna Hayward
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.89,0:12:25.24,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,云顿·厄尔干的.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.02,0:12:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from Windom Earle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.72,0:12:28.02,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你是说3个女孩\N都给厄尔盯上了?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.83,0:12:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean Earle's contacted\Nall three girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.41,0:12:31.37,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你肯定?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.56,0:12:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.72,0:12:37.72,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}看那山峰高耸入云,\N犹如波涛延绵不断{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.87,0:12:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See the mountains kiss high heaven\NAnd the waves clasp one another
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.89,0:12:42.85,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}没有一朵姐妹花会被宽恕\N如果它鄙视它的兄弟{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.00,0:12:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No sister-flower would be forgiven\Nlf it disdained its brother
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.98,0:12:46.19,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是我曾经送给凯若琳的一首诗.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.11,0:12:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A poem l once sent to Caroline.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.58,0:12:50.06,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望这不过\N是个嘲笑, 哈里.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.71,0:12:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l hope it's nothing more\Nthan a taunt, Harry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.58,0:12:55.28,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,厄尔喜欢用他的能力去伤及无辜性命\N以此来显示自己变态的自豪感.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.72,0:12:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Earle takes perverse pride in his ability\Nto insinuate himself into innocent lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.11,0:12:58.24,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那, 我们尽可能快的\N去找女孩们谈谈.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.22,0:12:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's talk to the girls\Nas soon as we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.41,0:12:59.89,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,看他们能记起些什么.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.56,0:13:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See what they remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.32,0:13:06.58,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,唐娜·海沃德的诗.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.46,0:13:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Donna Hayward's poem.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.02,0:13:13.15,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,欧蕊·荷恩在西雅图.\N明天之前不会回来.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.14,0:13:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Audrey Horne is in Seattle.\NShe won't be back till tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.32,0:13:16.06,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,布里格斯少校来了\N在会议室.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.47,0:13:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Major Briggs is here\Nin the conference room.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.24,0:13:17.80,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,豪克?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.38,0:13:17.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hawk?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.02,0:13:23.37,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,能麻烦你给我拿一下\N里欧·强生的逮捕报告?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.15,0:13:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you please bring me\NLeo Johnson's arrest report?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.37,0:13:26.71,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,里欧?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.49,0:13:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leo?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.85,0:13:29.24,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.99,0:13:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.50,0:13:34.50,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我要把碎片连起来, 哈里.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.62,0:13:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Putting the pieces together, Harry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.02,0:13:36.76,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,布伦南警官?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.16,0:13:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deputy Brennan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.93,0:13:39.19,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,据我记忆,\N你现在正画的这条线
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.06,0:13:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As l remember,\Nthe line you are drawing
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.37,0:13:41.54,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,应该一直沿着下方画,\N而不是打横.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.50,0:13:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,should proceed downward,\Nnot across.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.24,0:13:44.02,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎么知道的?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.37,0:13:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.24,0:13:48.23,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,布里格斯少校?\N感谢你的到来，先生.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.37,0:13:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Major Briggs?\NThank you, sir, for coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.15,0:13:52.63,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,少校, 我们需要你的帮助.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.28,0:13:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Major, we need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.80,0:13:56.50,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但我不能够准确的向你\N描述如何或为什么.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.95,0:13:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But l am unable to accurately\Ndescribe for you how or why.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.89,0:13:58.37,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,继续说.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.02,0:13:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.54,0:14:00.67,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,双峰警察局\N现在陷入了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.65,0:14:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Twin Peaks Sheriff's Department\Nis currently involved
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.84,0:14:02.76,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,几宗离奇的调查案中.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.99,0:14:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in several disparate investigations.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.41,0:14:06.15,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,被通缉的重罪犯里欧·强生\N失踪了.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.52,0:14:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The disappearance\Nof known felon, Leo Johnson.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.32,0:14:07.80,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我的前搭档\N兼杀人嫌疑犯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.46,0:14:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The appearance\Nof my former partner
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.97,0:14:10.15,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,云顿·厄尔,\N失踪了.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.09,0:14:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and suspected murderer,\NWindom Earle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.32,0:14:12.50,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,还有在一个叫猫头鹰山洞\N的地方发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.46,0:14:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the discovery of petroglyphs\Nof an unknown origin
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.67,0:14:13.84,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,一副来历不明的岩石壁画.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.80,0:14:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in a place called Owl Cave.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.02,0:14:15.97,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,现在, 按一般逻辑\N看来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.13,0:14:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, it would seem\Nlogic would dictate
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.15,0:14:19.32,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这些案子\N似乎都是单独分离的个案.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.30,0:14:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that these investigations\Nbe considered separate entities.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.50,0:14:21.50,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,然而, 我相信事情另有跷蹊.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.64,0:14:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, l believe otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.67,0:14:24.02,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我相信这一系列神秘事件\N并不是单独存在的,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.81,0:14:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l believe that these mysteries\Nare not separate entities,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.19,0:14:27.15,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,事实上, 它们不过是同一首诗上\N的补充诗句罢了.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.31,0:14:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but are in fact, complementary verses\Nof the same song.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.32,0:14:29.76,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,现在, 我尚未把它听的很真切.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.45,0:14:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, l cannot hear it yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.93,0:14:31.63,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但我已经能感觉到它了.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.05,0:14:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But l can feel it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.80,0:14:33.32,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那足够让我\N着手进行下去.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.95,0:14:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that is enough\Nfor me to proceed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.54,0:14:35.41,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我要怎么做才能真正帮助你呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.65,0:14:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How exactly may l help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.32,0:14:38.41,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我需要知道\N一切有关
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.46,0:14:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l need to know everything\Nthat there is to know
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.58,0:14:41.84,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,云顿·厄尔在参与\N蓝皮书项目时的事.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.72,0:14:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,about Windom Earle's work\Nwith Project Blue Book.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.02,0:14:45.02,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我失踪后，在高度机密安检的资格\N就被迅速撤销了.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.16,0:14:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My security clearance was revoked\Nshortly after my disappearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.23,0:14:48.36,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你有能力入侵\N蓝皮书档案吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.36,0:14:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And your ability to access\Nthese Blue Book files?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.02,0:14:51.54,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,现在, 问题不单在于入侵档案.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.17,0:14:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, the issue is not one of access.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.19,0:14:57.45,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,而是, 基于某些道德准则，\N我必须考虑.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.34,0:14:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, there are certain\Nmoral judgments l must consider.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.84,0:15:00.71,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是的, 先生, 我理解.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.98,0:15:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir, l understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.06,0:15:05.41,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这些信息能帮助你\N防止再有人伤亡吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.21,0:15:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will this information help you\Nto prevent future loss of life?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.63,0:15:07.02,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那当然了.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.75,0:15:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Most assuredly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.84,0:15:13.93,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这是你在猫头鹰山洞找到的\N那幅巖壁画的复制品吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.99,0:15:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ls this a copy of the petroglyph\Nyou found in Owl Cave?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.93,0:15:16.67,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,安迪?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.06,0:15:16.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Andy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.84,0:15:18.32,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,先生.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.00,0:15:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.32,0:15:20.45,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得这眼熟吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.47,0:15:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you familiar with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.93,0:15:22.89,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯, 我梦见过它.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.07,0:15:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, l've dreamed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.45,0:15:27.41,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,或者在某处见过它, 反正就见过.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.60,0:15:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or seen it somewhere, somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.15,0:15:53.15,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你会照你说的办.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.30,0:15:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l will do what you ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.50,0:15:59.49,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 里欧·强生的逮捕报告.\N- 干的好, 豪克.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.64,0:15:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Leo Johnson's arrest report.\N- Good work, Hawk.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.93,0:16:05.67,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,先生们,\N里欧·强生的脑损伤
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.08,0:16:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gentlemen,\Nthe damage to Leo Johnson
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.89,0:16:08.88,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,会改变某些\N书写特征.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.01,0:16:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,would alter\Ncertain handwriting characteristics.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.06,0:16:12.15,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,然而, 基本形态\N仍是一样的.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.22,0:16:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, the basic style\Nwould remain the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.45,0:16:26.19,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这首诗,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.60,0:16:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This poem,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.41,0:16:31.28,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是云顿·厄尔寄来的,\N由里欧·强生抄写.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.53,0:16:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,sent by Windom Earle,\Nwas transcribed by Leo Johnson.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.84,0:16:42.32,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,荷恩先生.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.98,0:16:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Horne.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.32,0:16:47.32,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,荷恩先生, 无疑你该知道,\N还有几小时
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.45,0:16:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Horne, as you are no doubt aware,\Nthere are but scant hours
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.49,0:16:49.36,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的品酒会马上就要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.62,0:16:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,until our wine-tasting benefit begins
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.54,0:16:53.01,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但我在哪儿都\N找不着你的女儿.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.66,0:16:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and l can't find\Nyour daughter anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.19,0:16:55.41,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,欧蕊要去西雅图一天
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.33,0:16:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Audrey is in Seattle for the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.62,0:17:00.28,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,可是, 我肯定我们的前台人员\N将会协助你.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.76,0:17:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, l'm sure that our concierge\Nwill be able to assist you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.45,0:17:02.02,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,前台人员.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.60,0:17:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The concierge.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.19,0:17:03.62,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是的, 这很重要.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.34,0:17:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.84,0:17:05.97,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你, 荷恩先生.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.97,0:17:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Mr. Horne.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.15,0:17:07.58,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,噢, ...先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.27,0:17:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Mr...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.02,0:17:10.32,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 理查·揣眉.\N- 揣眉, 是, 对.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.14,0:17:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Richard Tremayne.\N- Tremayne, yes, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.54,0:17:12.54,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 男装部.\N- 男装部, 好的.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.68,0:17:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Men's fashions.\N- Men's fashions, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.71,0:17:14.06,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.85,0:17:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.93,0:17:17.41,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你的鼻子怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.08,0:17:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,how is your nose?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.58,0:17:19.49,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哦, 荷恩先生, 不用担心，没事.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.72,0:17:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Mr. Horne, think nothing of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.67,0:17:24.36,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,一个鼻子，比起更伟大而美好的\N慈善服务，不过是一点小小付出.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.79,0:17:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A nose is a small price to pay\Nin the service of a greater good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.19,0:17:30.14,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那好, 当然由我们来\N支付所有医疗费用.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.33,0:17:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we will, of course,\Npay any medical expenses.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.54,0:17:32.84,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,真好.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.66,0:17:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.45,0:17:36.67,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,还有一件事\N员工的多种赔偿金
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.60,0:17:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One might also think\Nworkers' compensation
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.84,0:17:40.06,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,或许也应考虑在内.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.97,0:17:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in some variety will be involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.62,0:17:44.75,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那倒容易.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.74,0:17:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Easily done.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.97,0:17:48.06,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这也很重要的, 荷恩先生.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.11,0:17:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Capital, Mr. Horne.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.23,0:17:50.67,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我会提醒我的律师.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.38,0:17:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'll alert my attorney.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.36,0:17:57.27,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,"我要提醒我的律师."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.49,0:17:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,''l will alert my attorney.''
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.84,0:18:03.10,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,有时做坏事的冲动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.99,0:18:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes the urge to do bad
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.28,0:18:06.23,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,真的几乎是压倒性的.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.43,0:18:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is nearly overpowering.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.10,0:18:22.58,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,尽情喝吧, 我的朋友. 我们来庆祝.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.25,0:18:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drink up, my friend. We celebrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.36,0:18:28.14,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,庆祝?\N我的手臂都动不了.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.52,0:18:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Celebrate?\Nl can barely move my arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.62,0:18:33.58,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你这短暂的一生\N活的脏臭，阴暗又卑微.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.76,0:18:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have lived your short life\Nin odium and obscurity.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.75,0:18:36.27,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但现在, 人生的最后,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.89,0:18:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now, at the last,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.45,0:18:39.27,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你将会步上更大的舞台.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.60,0:18:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you will step upon the larger stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.45,0:18:42.10,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我得承认, 我羡慕你.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.60,0:18:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l must confess, l envy you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.27,0:18:44.75,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你的旅程远在想像\N之外的一点开始了.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.40,0:18:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your journey begins\Nat a point beyond imagining.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.93,0:18:47.49,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道它从那儿\N去到哪儿旅行?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.07,0:18:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows where it might travel\Nfrom there?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.67,0:18:49.45,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我快憋死了.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.81,0:18:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm pumped.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.62,0:18:53.62,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿, 这要干嘛, 像那个,\N参加什么紫丁香巡游吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.74,0:18:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, is this for, like,\Nthe Lilac Parade or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.80,0:18:56.49,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不, 不是巡游, 我的朋友,\N肯定不是.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.95,0:18:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not a parade, my friend,\Nnot exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.67,0:19:00.45,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那好, 能忙上的点忙，还有其他什么的\N我真的觉得挺酷的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.82,0:19:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, l'm real cool\Nabout helping out and everything
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.67,0:19:02.93,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但我怎么才能从这个东西里出来?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.79,0:19:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but how do l get out of this thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.10,0:19:05.10,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你不出来.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.26,0:19:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.27,0:19:07.10,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,里欧?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.39,0:19:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leo?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.27,0:19:09.80,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,给我箭.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.43,0:19:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fetch me an arrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.14,0:19:13.93,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,箭?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.30,0:19:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.58,0:19:17.32,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哇, 伙计.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.70,0:19:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.49,0:19:20.58,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我可不欣赏恶作剧.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.64,0:19:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l do not appreciate practical jokes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.75,0:19:25.01,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,里欧, 箭?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.91,0:19:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leo, the arrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.80,0:19:29.23,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.91,0:19:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.19,0:19:36.27,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,呀, 别电击那怪胎.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.32,0:19:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, don't zap the geek.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.49,0:19:38.84,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,没有他我怎么\N喝我的啤酒啊--? 你知道么.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.62,0:19:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How am l supposed to get\Nmy beer without--? You know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.27,0:19:43.49,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哥们. 那很痛吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.43,0:19:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dude. That hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.45,0:19:49.88,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,给我箭.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.60,0:19:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fetch me the arrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.53,0:20:07.97,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你, 里欧.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.68,0:20:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Leo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.27,0:20:14.84,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,箭干嘛用, 伙计?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.39,0:20:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with the arrow, man?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.88,0:20:17.84,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你要干嘛?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.03,0:20:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.27,0:20:20.88,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这可不好玩.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.40,0:20:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.58,0:20:24.71,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 安静.\N- 喂, 你到底要搞什么鬼啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.70,0:20:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Be still.\N- Well, what the hell are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.62,0:20:28.05,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,想想所有不幸的罪人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.77,0:20:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think of all the hapless sinners
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.23,0:20:31.32,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,都想知道哪里才是\N他们灵魂栖息的最终目的地.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.37,0:20:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,wondering where\Ntheir souls' destination lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.92,0:20:33.58,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,为了什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.08,0:20:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.79,0:20:36.23,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,就是为了得到\N一个简单问题的答案.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.91,0:20:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To gain the answer\Nto a simple question.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.40,0:20:40.75,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我的灵魂将会在哪里甦醒?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.55,0:20:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where will my spirit awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.23,0:20:45.01,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我死后又会去到何种世界呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.39,0:20:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What life am l given after this life?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.92,0:20:52.75,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这个死魂灵一样的问题，如瘟疫般\N永远折磨着人那颗可怜的良心.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.06,0:20:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This grave question has plagued\Nman's sorry conscience for eons.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.92,0:20:56.27,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,而现在, 你, 你这幸运男孩.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.07,0:20:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now, you, you lucky boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.75,0:20:59.45,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你即将揭晓答案了.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.87,0:20:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.19,0:21:01.45,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,马上.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.34,0:21:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.05,0:21:15.53,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,双峰小姐\N裁判规章委员会现在开会.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.19,0:21:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Twin Peaks Judging and Rules\NCommittee is now in session.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.71,0:21:19.97,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道么, 今年将会\N非常令人兴奋.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.85,0:21:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, this year\Nis going to be very exciting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.45,0:21:22.92,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 现在，我们--\N- 非常兴奋.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.59,0:21:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Now we--\N- Very exciting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.10,0:21:25.44,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,今年将会\N非常，非常令人兴奋.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.23,0:21:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This year is going to be\Nvery, very exciting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.62,0:21:27.10,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你, 杜恩.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.76,0:21:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Dwayne.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.27,0:21:29.05,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,现在, 第一件事.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.40,0:21:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, first order of business.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.23,0:21:31.45,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,本·荷恩先生已请求\N以委员会之友的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.37,0:21:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Ben Horne has asked\Nto address the committee
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.62,0:21:33.14,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,向委员会之辞.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.77,0:21:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as a friend of the committee.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.32,0:21:36.45,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我对此没有异议.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.47,0:21:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l don't have any objection to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.62,0:21:39.14,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,请致辞, 本.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.74,0:21:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Address away, Ben.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.32,0:21:40.92,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.45,0:21:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.79,0:21:46.71,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这, 杜恩, 让我先恭喜你\N新近订婚.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.91,0:21:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And, Dwayne, let me congratulate you\Non your recent engagement.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.79,0:21:49.49,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢你.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.95,0:21:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.71,0:21:52.97,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,她是一个可爱的女人\N我祝愿你幸福无比.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.86,0:21:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a lovely woman\Nand l wish you much happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.14,0:21:56.27,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,真的, 非常感谢你.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.29,0:21:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.23,0:21:59.92,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,先生们.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.36,0:22:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.71,0:22:02.44,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我的意图很简单.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.87,0:22:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My purpose is simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.62,0:22:08.53,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,以往那些挤眉弄眼, 穿着泳装乱颤颠\N的选美节早已过时了.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.77,0:22:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The age of the ogling, swim-suited\Njiggle festivals of the past is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.10,0:22:12.49,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,而双峰小姐, 我相信,\N是端庄的,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.24,0:22:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Twin Peaks, l believe,\Nand rightly,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.10,0:22:18.97,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,现在，这是一个展示全体女性\N素质的庆典.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.25,0:22:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is now a celebration\Nof the totality of a woman's qualities.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.14,0:22:22.14,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,美要被赋予\N一个更广泛的定义
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.28,0:22:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beauty has taken on\Na broader definition
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.31,0:22:27.53,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,包括才智, 精神境界, 价值观, 创意.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.45,0:22:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to include mind, spirit, values, ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.75,0:22:30.79,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,基于这些, 先生们,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.89,0:22:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And for taking this step, gentlemen,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.97,0:22:32.18,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我为你们鼓掌喝彩.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.10,0:22:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l applaud you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.14,0:22:36.71,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他这是在推销什么?\N你在推销什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.30,0:22:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's he selling?\NWhat are you selling?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.88,0:22:38.40,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,市长先生, 我就不妨\N直说了吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.00,0:22:38.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Mayor, let me get\Nright to the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.88,0:22:41.79,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,双峰小姐是一件大事\N要为此搜索一个主题.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.00,0:22:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Twin Peaks is an event\Nin search of a theme.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.97,0:22:43.88,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那, 我提议很简单.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.11,0:22:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, what l propose is simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.05,0:22:51.31,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,今年演讲的主题应该是\N如何拯救我们的森林.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.18,0:22:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The topic of this year's speeches\Nshould be how to save our forests.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.01,0:22:58.88,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,符合潮流, 切题,有意义\N全球化，还有就是...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.15,0:22:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's now, it's relevant,\Nit's global and it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.79,0:23:03.23,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,要么, 更清楚地说,\N先生们, 就是我们.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.93,0:23:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, to put it plainly,\Ngentlemen, it's us.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.84,0:23:10.57,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,明摆着, 你就是要和\N格斯伍发展计划对着干
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.00,0:23:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, your opposition\Nto the Ghostwood development plans
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.75,0:23:13.01,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,除此之外\N就没别的了?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.87,0:23:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,wouldn't have anything\Nto do with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.18,0:23:14.88,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,皮特,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.31,0:23:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pete,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.84,0:23:18.75,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我讨厌你这话的弦外之音.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.97,0:23:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l resent your implication.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.92,0:23:24.05,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这里的环境问题可能\N阻碍了一些本地的经济
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.04,0:23:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The environmental issues here\Ndwarf any parochial business concerns
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.23,0:23:29.10,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但这关系到你，我，他
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.35,0:23:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that l, or you, or anyone else
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.31,0:23:31.05,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,任何一个人都脱不开.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.46,0:23:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,might be pursuing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.23,0:23:34.70,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们对此会从长计议的.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.36,0:23:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll take it under advisement.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.88,0:23:37.36,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们对此会从长计议的.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.03,0:23:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll take it under advisement.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.57,0:23:39.40,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那是我全部\N的冀望了.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.73,0:23:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the most\Nthat l could hope for.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.57,0:23:43.92,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,先生们, 谢谢你们的宝贵时间.\N市长先生.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.73,0:23:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gentlemen, thank you for your time.\NMr. Mayor.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.27,0:23:49.01,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他以为他能装神弄鬼.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.41,0:23:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He thinks he can pull a fast one.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.18,0:23:51.27,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这个想法有其价值.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.34,0:23:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The idea has merit.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.44,0:23:53.05,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这个想法有其价值.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.58,0:23:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The idea has merit.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.23,0:23:54.88,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我个人倒赞成这意见.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.38,0:23:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm in favor of it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.92,0:23:59.14,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 波比.\N- 嘿, 领导.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.05,0:23:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Bobby.\N- Hey, chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.36,0:24:01.53,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,别忘了\N去干洗的事儿, 好吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.49,0:24:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget\Nthe dry-cleaning, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.70,0:24:03.22,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.85,0:24:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.01,0:24:15.62,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,第一位候选人\N麻烦到委员会这来
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.13,0:24:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will the first candidate\Nplease approach the committee?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.79,0:24:19.57,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,拉娜? 过来吧, 小蜜糖.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.93,0:24:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lana? Come on up, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.57,0:24:33.79,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这不搞关系吗，没人管吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.72,0:24:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does anybody smell a fix here?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.96,0:24:36.66,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我办不到, 波比.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.09,0:24:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l can't do this, Bobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.88,0:24:39.75,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我这辈子，从来没发表过\N演说.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.02,0:24:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l have never made a speech before\Nin my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.92,0:24:42.92,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我四年级，在班上的加德纳太太面前\N读过一份书报告
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.06,0:24:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l read a book report in the fourth grade\Nin front of Mrs. Gardner's class
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.09,0:24:45.48,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,然后就在全班面前\N昏过去了.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.23,0:24:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and l passed out\Nright in front of the whole room.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.66,0:24:49.53,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你会做的很棒的, 宝贝娃娃.\N我会帮你做讲辞写手.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.80,0:24:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll do great, doll.\Nl'm gonna be your speech writer.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.57,0:24:54.09,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你一定会很棒的.\N别担心, 好吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.74,0:24:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna be great.\NDon't worry, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.92,0:25:02.18,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,-给你. 祝好运.\N-唐娜? 你也来报名吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.08,0:25:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-Here you go. Good luck.\N-Donna? Are you entering too?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.40,0:25:06.22,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 是啊, 你也是?\N- 噢, 我绝不会错过.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.55,0:25:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Yeah, you too?\N- Oh, l wouldn't miss it for the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.40,0:25:08.92,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 这不很令人兴奋吗?\N- 就是.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.55,0:25:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- lsn't it exciting?\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.09,0:25:10.70,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,就是.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.25,0:25:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.05,0:25:15.05,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,迈克, 好长一段时间没见了.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.19,0:25:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mike, it's a long time no see.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.22,0:25:18.83,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我本来想问你跑哪儿去了\N但我想我现在知道了.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.36,0:25:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'd ask where you've been\Nkeeping yourself but l think l know.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.01,0:25:22.40,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 这真的很吓人哦, 迈克.\N- 并不像你想的那样.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.13,0:25:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- This is very scary, Mike.\N- lt's not what you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.57,0:25:25.49,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不像我想的那样.\N你怎么知道我怎么想?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.70,0:25:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's not what l think.\NWhat do you think l think?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.66,0:25:27.61,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你在想我和一个\N老女人约会.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.80,0:25:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think l'm going out\Nwith an older woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.05,0:25:34.14,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我在想不知你突然哪儿来的兴趣\N竟然过起了化石生涯.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.21,0:25:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l think l don't know where you got this\Nsudden interest in the life of fossils.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.35,0:25:36.22,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊, 但...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.48,0:25:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.44,0:25:37.70,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这真不是你想的那样.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.58,0:25:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's not what you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.09,0:25:41.66,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,迈克, 拜托了.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.22,0:25:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mike, big favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.83,0:25:44.09,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,给我讲个明白吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.99,0:25:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clear this up for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.31,0:25:46.79,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会期望你理解.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.46,0:25:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l wouldn't expect you to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.01,0:25:49.48,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我会努力去理解的.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.16,0:25:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l will strive to be understanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.35,0:25:54.57,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你有没有试想过
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.50,0:25:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any idea
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.75,0:25:57.01,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,一个性成熟和神力
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.90,0:25:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,what a combination of sexual maturity
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.18,0:26:00.09,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,的结合体\N能导致什么结果吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.30,0:26:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and superhuman strength\Ncan result in?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.09,0:26:11.66,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.22,0:26:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.31,0:26:38.96,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,凯萨琳, 如果你能\N告诉我有关她的, 任何事--
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.44,0:26:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Catherine, if there's anything\Nyou can tell me about her, anything--
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.14,0:26:42.22,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,什么都好\N反正能帮我理解整件事的.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.28,0:26:42.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything at all\Nthat might help me understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.40,0:26:44.14,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,比如?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.55,0:26:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For instance?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.74,0:26:48.05,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是什么\N令她做出那些事的?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.88,0:26:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What made her do\Nthe things she did?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.22,0:26:50.40,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,在她背后又是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.35,0:26:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was she after?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.57,0:26:54.14,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这些问题\N我也问过自己很多遍了.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.72,0:26:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l've been asking myself\Na lot of the same things.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.70,0:26:55.74,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,凯萨琳?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.86,0:26:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Catherine?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.14,0:26:58.31,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我需要去理解它.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.26,0:26:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l need to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.05,0:27:03.79,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我想在她早年的生涯里,\N她肯定是学到什么教训
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.20,0:27:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l think that early in her life,\Nshe must have learned the lesson
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.96,0:27:09.01,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,以致她认为要生存\N就必须伪装成别人想看到,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.10,0:27:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that she could survive by being\Nwhat other people wanted to see,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.18,0:27:11.83,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,得到的东西.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.31,0:27:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by showing them that.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.18,0:27:15.92,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,至于她私己的真面目\N到底还剩下多少,就难说了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.31,0:27:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And whatever was left\Nof her private self,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.09,0:27:18.48,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,她或许从未给任何人\N展示过.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.25,0:27:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she may never have shown\Nto anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.66,0:27:23.09,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 那么，她以前说的那些故事, 谎言都是--?\N- 哦, 天晓得?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.82,0:27:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- So all the stories, the lies were--?\N- Well, who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.27,0:27:26.31,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,对她来说，它们不见得\N不真实啊.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.42,0:27:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They may not have seemed\Nuntrue to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.35,0:27:32.61,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,随机应变\N是她永远的信条.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.49,0:27:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What she needed to believe was\Nalways shifting to suit the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.66,0:27:37.66,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,尽管她试图对我和我的家族\N做了那些坏事,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.80,0:27:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ln spite of all the things\Nshe tried to do to me and my family,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.83,0:27:40.79,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但我却好奇的发现\N很难为此而恨她.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.97,0:27:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l find it curiously hard\Nto hate her for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.05,0:27:44.13,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哦, 她是...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.21,0:27:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, she was...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.35,0:27:46.31,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,她是如此如此的美丽.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.51,0:27:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was so very beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.35,0:27:59.66,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这儿有条线索\N或许能对我们俩有帮助.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.49,0:27:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There may be a clue\Nthat could benefit both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.83,0:28:01.57,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.99,0:28:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.09,0:28:08.31,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,托马斯·埃卡死的时候\N留了这个给我.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.23,0:28:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thomas Eckhardt left this to me\Nwhen he died.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.48,0:28:11.26,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,它的出现让我觉得这可能\N和乔西有什么关系.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.63,0:28:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt occurred to me that it might have\Nsomething to do with Josie.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.44,0:28:12.87,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,里面是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.60,0:28:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.09,0:28:16.31,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道.\N我一直无法打开它.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.24,0:28:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l don't know.\Nl haven't been able to open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.48,0:28:18.18,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,让我看看.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.64,0:28:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.00,0:28:23.40,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 啊, 没盖子, 没--\N- 没.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.15,0:28:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Well, there's no lid, there's--\N- No.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.61,0:28:26.18,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,也没扣子.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.75,0:28:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no clasp.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.35,0:28:28.22,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哇喂, 波波.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.49,0:28:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wowee, Bob.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.39,0:28:33.13,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经有很多美女\N来参加今年的比赛了.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.55,0:28:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have we got some beauties\Nin the contest this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.31,0:28:34.35,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你好, 哈里.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.46,0:28:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Harry.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.53,0:28:38.40,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好像镇上的每个少女\N都来排队准备要大秀一番--
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.66,0:28:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like every gal in town\Nis lined up to take a shot at the--
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.61,0:28:43.00,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,快说, 够运气把\N这东西打开吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.76,0:28:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, have you had any luck\Nwith this thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.66,0:28:46.39,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,笨手笨脚.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.80,0:28:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Butterfingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.66,0:28:55.09,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我的圣魔草啊.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.81,0:28:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Holy moly.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.26,0:28:56.92,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.41,0:28:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.66,0:29:09.39,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 给我.\N- 等等, 小松狮.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.82,0:29:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Give it to me.\N- Just a second, poodle.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.74,0:29:21.65,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,别紧张, 我只是拿着它而已.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.87,0:29:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, l held it just so.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.61,0:29:47.26,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,以前，我每个夏天都在这游泳.\N一周游2，3次.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.76,0:29:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l used to swim here every summer.\NTwo or three times a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.74,0:29:51.39,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那我选对地方了.\N这儿真美.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.90,0:29:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then l made a good choice.\Nlt's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.31,0:29:55.31,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我总是觉得大自然比人\N要亲近的多了.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.47,0:29:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l always felt closer to nature\Nthan l did to people.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.48,0:29:59.00,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 为什么?\N- 我从来没有太多朋友.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.64,0:29:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Why?\N- l never had many friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.18,0:30:01.61,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,而诺玛却是大众情人.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.34,0:30:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Norma was always Miss Popularity.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.78,0:30:03.87,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,她总是轻易就\N能面对外界.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.95,0:30:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was always moving\Ntoward the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.09,0:30:05.61,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,而我却正好\N相反.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.22,0:30:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And l was always\Nmoving away from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.79,0:30:09.48,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 大多时候, 我都活在自己的世界里.\N- 那样的社区不坏嘛.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.95,0:30:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Lived in my head, mostly.\N- That's not a bad neighborhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.35,0:30:13.00,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但有些奇怪的\N邻居.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.49,0:30:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's some pretty strange\Nneighbors.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.65,0:30:16.74,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 有很多男友吗?\N- 没有.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.79,0:30:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Many boyfriends?\N- No.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.91,0:30:17.96,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,真的?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.06,0:30:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.09,0:30:21.00,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,对, 我有过一个.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.23,0:30:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, l had one.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.13,0:30:22.39,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,高中?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.30,0:30:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,High school?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.57,0:30:23.70,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,大学.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.73,0:30:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senior year.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.87,0:30:28.74,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是什么原因\N会让你跑到修道院里去?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.00,0:30:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have anything to do\Nwith why you went into the convent?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.74,0:30:33.87,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思, 我不想谈这个，\N你介意吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.88,0:30:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm sorry, do you mind\Nif we don't talk about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.13,0:30:38.78,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系.\N随你喜欢，我们以后再谈吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.28,0:30:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.\NWe can talk about whatever you'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.00,0:30:42.87,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我想回到现实生活中来.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.15,0:30:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l wanna come back to the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.05,0:30:44.96,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我受惊太长时间了.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.19,0:30:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l was so frightened for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.13,0:30:47.61,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我理解.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.29,0:30:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.35,0:30:51.05,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,逃避并不是办法\N恐惧是不会因此而消失的.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.49,0:30:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiding from your fear\Ndoesn't make your fear go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.61,0:30:54.78,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,反倒令它更强烈.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.76,0:30:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Makes it stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.26,0:30:59.83,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我必须面对它.\N亲自去面对它.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.40,0:31:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So l had to face it.\Nl had to face myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.00,0:31:03.74,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,而且我必须在这直面它.\N因为这里就是出错的地方.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.17,0:31:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And l had to do it here.\NWhere everything went so wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.87,0:31:19.04,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,安妮, 我知道事情看来\N有多么的无望.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.02,0:31:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Annie, l know how hopeless\Nthings can seem.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.18,0:31:24.83,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你坠入\N了黑暗的隧道.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.33,0:31:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l know about the dark tunnel\Nyou can fall into.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.00,0:31:26.35,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我离开之前发生的.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.13,0:31:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt happened before l went away.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.13,0:31:29.39,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,为了那个男孩.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.30,0:31:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt happened because of that boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.74,0:31:34.70,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,在我身上发生过类似的事.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.87,0:31:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something similar happened to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.87,0:31:37.00,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,它简直让我想从此\N消失在世上.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.01,0:31:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt made me wanna disappear\Nfrom the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.83,0:31:41.48,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,正因为如此,\N或许我能帮助你.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.98,0:31:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of that,\Nmaybe l can help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.04,0:31:57.04,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我对你还不是很了解.\N- 不了解.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.19,0:31:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- l don't know you very well.\N- No.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.57,0:32:00.96,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我正试着学会\N如何去相信我的直觉.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.73,0:32:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm trying to learn\Nhow to trust my instincts.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.74,0:32:04.91,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那它们怎么说?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.90,0:32:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are they saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.44,0:32:09.35,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,信任.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.61,0:32:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.52,0:33:17.78,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好. 晚上好, 各位.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.67,0:33:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening. Evening, all.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.96,0:33:21.43,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎来到\N我们的评酒晚宴.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.11,0:33:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And welcome\Nto our oenophiliac soiree.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.61,0:33:24.48,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,在持续不断的系列\N公共活动中,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.78,0:33:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another in a continuing series\Nof public events,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.65,0:33:26.74,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这又是一个由荷恩企业赞助的,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.78,0:33:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,sponsored by Horne lndustries,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.91,0:33:32.00,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,有益于停止格斯伍发展计划\N的举措.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.09,0:33:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to benefit the Stop Ghostwood\NDevelopment movement.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.22,0:33:34.30,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,品什么东西?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.36,0:33:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ono-what?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.48,0:33:37.95,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 可能是葡萄酒吧.\N- 那么,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.63,0:33:38.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Something to do with wine.\N- And now,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.30,0:33:40.22,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,品尝开始了.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.46,0:33:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to the tasting.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.43,0:33:44.04,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,拉娜, 露西,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.60,0:33:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lana, Lucy,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.22,0:33:47.13,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你们愿意帮我倒酒吗, 劳驾了.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.37,0:33:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if you'd like to help me pour, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.30,0:34:01.52,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚我们品尝的第一款\N是红葡萄酒.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.45,0:34:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our first wines this evening\Nare reds.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.69,0:34:05.17,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,有些学派\N他们会说,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.85,0:34:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are some schools of thought\Nwho, of course, say,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.39,0:34:08.48,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,除了红葡萄酒之外，其他都不能算葡萄酒.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.52,0:34:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there are no other wines but reds.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.69,0:34:10.30,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,请说, 安迪?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.83,0:34:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Andy?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.48,0:34:15.69,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道还有白葡萄酒\N和气泡酒.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.63,0:34:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are also white wines\Nand sparkling wines.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.00,0:34:18.87,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你, 安迪.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.17,0:34:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Andy.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.00,0:34:22.48,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,现在我们杯里都倒进酒了,\N让我们首先来尝试--
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.17,0:34:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now that we're all poured,\Nlet us first examine--
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.65,0:34:24.65,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,还没开始呢, 安迪,\N看在老天爷的份上.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.81,0:34:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't taste it yet, Andy,\Nfor heaven's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.87,0:34:26.26,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,吐出来.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.01,0:34:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spit it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.78,0:34:31.04,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.91,0:34:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.26,0:34:33.91,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.42,0:34:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.61,0:34:37.21,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们来这, 就是为了学习.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.75,0:34:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what we're here for, to learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.91,0:34:39.82,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好了, 回到酒上.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.06,0:34:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, to the wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.26,0:34:43.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们必须先用鼻子\N去鉴别酒香
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.39,0:34:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We must first examine\Nthe nose of the wine
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.74,0:34:46.82,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,看它能否告诉我们\N什么花香蕴含在里面.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.90,0:34:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to see what it can tell us\Nabout its bouquet.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.00,0:34:49.69,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,而我们要用什么才能做到呢...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.17,0:34:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we do that by...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.17,0:34:52.43,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,用嗅觉.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.34,0:34:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By smelling.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.04,0:34:56.74,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,非常好, 拉娜.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.17,0:34:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very good, Lana.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.30,0:35:06.39,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,举起玻璃杯, 这样.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.45,0:35:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lift the glass, thusly.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.56,0:35:09.69,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,然后，当我们用力\N晃杯的同时,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.72,0:35:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And while rolling the wine\Nvigorously around in the glass,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.87,0:35:14.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,深满的呼吸酒香.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.02,0:35:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we breathe deeply and fully.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.78,0:35:23.26,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,很好.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.93,0:35:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.43,0:35:29.95,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那现在, 我们品尝第一口,\N猛烈汹涌的吞一大口.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.57,0:35:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now, we take our first taste,\Na big boisterous gulp.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.17,0:35:32.61,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,然后让它在我们的\N整个颚腔中翻腾.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.31,0:35:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we roll it around\Nour entire palate.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.78,0:35:34.00,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们试着让
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.94,0:35:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we try to reach
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.21,0:35:38.78,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这些小味蕾仅仅延伸\N到舌根后面就够了,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.38,0:35:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,those little taste buds stuck\Nway far at the back of the tongue,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.04,0:35:41.13,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,记住不要吞下去哦.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.18,0:35:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,remembering not to swallow.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.34,0:35:43.13,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,太出色了.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.49,0:35:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.26,0:35:47.34,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好了, 吐出来.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.42,0:35:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now, we spit.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.04,0:35:56.08,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,于是，他从暗处慢慢走出,\N把死女孩扔在身后.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.20,0:35:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he came slowly out of the shadows,\Nleaving the dead girl behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.26,0:36:00.34,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,然后我说, "你在向前一步\N我就让你开天窗."
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.40,0:36:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And l said, ''You take one more step\Nand l will ventilate you.''
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.56,0:36:01.87,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,然后发生了什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.71,0:36:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.04,0:36:05.26,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,一个简短但感人的葬礼.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.21,0:36:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt was a brief, but touching funeral.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.87,0:36:09.30,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,戴尔, 真高兴赶得及见上你一面.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.01,0:36:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dale, glad l caught up with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.47,0:36:12.30,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,出租车正在外面等着呢\N我马上要上路了.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.65,0:36:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got the rental fired up outside\Nand about ready to hit the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.47,0:36:15.34,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,戈登, 超级棒\N你离开前能被我们赶上.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.62,0:36:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gordon, super\Nwe caught you before you left.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.56,0:36:17.60,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你快回来.\N- 我会的, 库.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.72,0:36:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- You hurry back.\N- l will, Coop.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.34,0:36:20.30,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 还记的安妮吗?\N- 我当然记的.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.49,0:36:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Remember Annie?\N- Of course l do.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.47,0:36:24.17,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,看来，这个双峰镇\N到处都是美人啊.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.63,0:36:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This world of Twin Peaks seems\Nto be filled with beautiful women.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.34,0:36:26.87,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我只能听见一个美人的话.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.50,0:36:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although only one l can hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.69,0:36:29.30,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,坐下和我们一起吃馅饼.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.83,0:36:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Join us for pie.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.13,0:36:31.69,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,乐意至极.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.30,0:36:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Love to.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.78,0:36:36.26,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 安妮?\N- 谢谢.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.94,0:36:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Annie?\N- Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.95,0:36:43.86,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,3人份.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.11,0:36:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three each.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.04,0:36:47.91,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 雪莉, 介意我们俩分享一个吗?\N- 不介意.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.18,0:36:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Shelly, do you mind if we share?\N- No.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.08,0:36:51.13,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,库, 常言道\N爱让世界转动.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.25,0:36:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coop, they say that love\Nmakes the world go around.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.30,0:36:55.21,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,谁能获其所需\N谁就是这世上最幸运的人.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.46,0:36:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Makes people who need people\Nthe luckiest people in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.39,0:37:00.04,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然从来没人说过\N这事他妈的还能治愈失聪呢.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.53,0:37:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although they never said a doggoned\Nthing about a cure for hearing loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.21,0:37:03.04,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,雪莉, 你真是个神迹使者.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.37,0:37:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shelly, you are a miracle worker.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.26,0:37:06.47,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,天僊下凡.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.40,0:37:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And a goddess sent from heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.69,0:37:08.00,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我不过是餐厅里的一个女招待.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.84,0:37:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm a waitress in a diner.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.17,0:37:10.34,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,之前，我从未被人\N比喻过天僊.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.34,0:37:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l've never been compared\Nto a goddess before.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.52,0:37:12.73,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这样, 雪莉,\N你只是还不知道自身的价值.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.68,0:37:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Shelly,\Nyou just don't know your own value.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.91,0:37:17.60,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,库, 她真是一个珍稀尤物\N你不觉得吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.04,0:37:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coop, she's a rare and precious\Nindividual, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.78,0:37:19.04,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我懂你的意思, 戈登.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.92,0:37:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l know what you mean, Gordon.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.69,0:37:25.25,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,雪莉, 在我失去勇气前\N转过来面对着我一会儿.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.85,0:37:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shelly, turn around and face me\Na moment before l lose my nerve.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.43,0:37:27.47,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我马上就要\N离开双峰镇了,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.59,0:37:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm about ready\Nto leave Twin Peaks,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.69,0:37:30.21,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道\N什么时候才会再回来.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.86,0:37:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and l don't know\Nwhen l'm gonna return.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.39,0:37:31.91,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但我想你知道\N能遇见你
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.53,0:37:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But l want you to know\Nthat meeting you
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.08,0:37:33.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,简直是莫大的恩赐.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.23,0:37:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,has been more than a privilege.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.21,0:37:35.91,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这让我心潮澎湃.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.37,0:37:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's touched my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.08,0:37:38.99,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道\N如果这一刻我不吻你,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.23,0:37:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And l know\Nthat if l don't kiss you now,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.21,0:37:42.99,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我将后悔\N终身.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.37,0:37:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm gonna regret it\Nthe rest of my days.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.26,0:37:45.73,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.41,0:37:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.47,0:37:49.86,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这算是哪门子事儿啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.61,0:37:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.04,0:37:53.04,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,开戏才刚开头呢,\N还有四分之三
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.21,0:37:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are a witnessing a front,\Nthree-quarter view
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.21,0:37:55.73,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,2个成年人分享柔情一刻\N的好戏在后头，有你看的.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.35,0:37:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of two adults\Nsharing a tender moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.73,0:37:58.60,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那反应，好像他之前\N从没见过人接吻似的.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.89,0:37:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Acts like he's never seen\Na kiss before.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.04,0:38:02.52,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,戈登?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.19,0:38:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gordon?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.69,0:38:06.47,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,再看看清楚咯, 傻小子,\N又来了.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.86,0:38:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take another look, sonny,\Nit's gonna happen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.91,0:38:16.04,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好了, 同学们,\N刚啜的那一小口向我们透露了些什么呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.07,0:38:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, class,\Nwhat did that sip reveal for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.21,0:38:18.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们正享受着什么味道呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.37,0:38:18.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What flavors are we enjoying?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.91,0:38:22.08,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,有点木的口味.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.04,0:38:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tastes kind of woody.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.56,0:38:25.60,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不, 事实上不是.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.71,0:38:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.78,0:38:28.60,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,还有谁回答? 拉娜?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.95,0:38:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone else? Lana?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.95,0:38:34.43,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 香蕉?\N- 对了.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.09,0:38:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Banana?\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.60,0:38:38.30,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,有香蕉作点缀的意味.\N那是一种模仿香蕉味的化学合成酸.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.76,0:38:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is a hint of banana.\NThat's the metachloric acid.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.47,0:38:39.65,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,很好.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.63,0:38:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.99,0:38:44.21,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 还有什么?\N- 香蕉.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.17,0:38:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- What else?\N- Banana.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.43,0:38:45.78,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,巧克力.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.57,0:38:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.99,0:38:47.69,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,正确, 安迪.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.14,0:38:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Correct, Andy.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.91,0:38:51.43,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,喝香蕉味酒，这不多此一举吗，\N我们干吗不直接去吃香蕉船呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.07,0:38:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we just skip the wine\Nand have a banana split?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.60,0:38:56.65,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,让我们来啜另一口, 好吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.78,0:38:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's take another sip, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.82,0:39:01.60,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这次吞掉,\N看还有什么我们能分辨出来的.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.98,0:39:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Swallowing this time,\Nand see what else we can discern.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.65,0:39:06.95,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们还能尝出其它味道吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.79,0:39:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What else can we taste?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.08,0:39:10.04,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,还有其它什么奇妙的味道\N在取悦着你的味蕾呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.26,0:39:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What other wonder\Ninvites taste buds toward pleasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.25,0:39:11.69,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,天啊, 基巴.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.40,0:39:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gosh, Dick.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.86,0:39:16.95,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,唔, 我从来都不知道\N酒原来有这么多不同的特质.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.03,0:39:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, l just never knew wine\Ncould have so many different qualities.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.12,0:39:22.38,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,神奇吧, 不是吗?\N一款真正的好酒就如同一个交响乐.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.27,0:39:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's amazing, isn't it?\NA really good wine is like a symphony.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.69,0:39:29.47,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你有什么感觉, 露西?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.84,0:39:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what is your reaction, Lucy?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.86,0:39:38.47,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我是孕妇.\N本就不该喝酒.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.02,0:39:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm pregnant.\Nl'm not supposed to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.34,0:40:05.17,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,爱是地狱.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.48,0:40:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Love is hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.64,0:40:08.21,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.82,0:40:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.38,0:40:11.16,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,爱, 简直就是地狱.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.55,0:40:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Love, it's hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.69,0:40:16.17,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,印度教徒说,\N爱是天堂之梯.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.86,0:40:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Hindus say,\Nlove is a ladder to heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.95,0:40:21.25,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他们还常常赤足\N行走在火炭上，以此为乐
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.10,0:40:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Hindus have also been known\Nto take hikes on hot coals
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.43,0:40:23.38,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,并因此而闻名.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.60,0:40:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for recreational purposes.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.56,0:40:25.25,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那是一种自律.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.70,0:40:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Self-discipline.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.08,0:40:28.25,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,自律和爱?\N好不搭调.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.24,0:40:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Self-discipline and love?\NThere's a bad match.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.43,0:40:30.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,世俗之爱.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.61,0:40:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Earthly love.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.30,0:40:31.86,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,还有其它的选择吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.48,0:40:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What other kind is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.03,0:40:33.51,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,当你入世了,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.21,0:40:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you're in it,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.73,0:40:35.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,就别无选择.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.88,0:40:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,no other.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.08,0:40:38.77,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那感觉就像给18铜人痛打了一顿,\N却仍未得到解脱，对吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.25,0:40:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt hits you like an 1 8-wheeler,\Ndoesn't it? And there's no relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.95,0:40:40.25,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那只会让你感到更真切.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.12,0:40:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt makes you feel more alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.43,0:40:42.69,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,让你对一切都感到\N更真切.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.59,0:40:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt makes you feel more\Nof everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.86,0:40:43.95,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,包括痛苦.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.02,0:40:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pain included.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.95,0:40:47.38,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,尤其是痛苦.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.09,0:40:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.08,0:40:52.60,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我控制不住要去想她.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.23,0:40:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l can't stop thinking about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.77,0:40:54.77,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,听来你的情况\N颇严重.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.93,0:40:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like\Nyou've got a pretty serious case.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.95,0:40:57.25,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哥们, 我心乱如麻,\N魂牵梦绕又刻骨铭心.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.10,0:40:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, l'm roped,\Ntied and branded.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.43,0:40:59.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,她有同样的感觉吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.57,0:40:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She feel the same way?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.34,0:41:02.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,希望是.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.51,0:41:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's hoping.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.73,0:41:07.38,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那你呢?\N你也上了黑名单?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.91,0:41:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about you?\NYou on the critical list too?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.47,0:41:11.73,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉我的心\N给人用撬棍一下子撬开了.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.61,0:41:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Feels like someone's taking\Na crowbar to my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.90,0:41:13.77,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿, 那不赖嘛.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.05,0:41:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that's not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.95,0:41:17.90,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不赖, 我想它也被封锁的\N够久了.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.12,0:41:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, l think it's been locked away\Nlong enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.51,0:41:20.25,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那是好事.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.66,0:41:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.43,0:41:22.29,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 希望是.\N- 敬你的.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.59,0:41:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Here's hoping.\N- Here's to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.12,0:41:29.43,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 维乐先生? 你的电报, 先生.\N- 谢谢你.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.30,0:41:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Mr. Wheeler? Telegram for you, sir.\N- Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.16,0:41:34.16,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢你.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.34,0:41:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.30,0:41:41.77,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,真该死.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.44,0:41:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.03,0:41:44.73,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 服务生?\N- 是的, 先生.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.18,0:41:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Bellman?\N- Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.95,0:41:46.90,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦你转告前台\N我要退房.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.12,0:41:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kindly tell the front desk\Nl'll be checking out.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.08,0:41:49.38,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 是, 先生.\N- 谢谢你.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.25,0:41:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Yes, sir.\N- Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.82,0:41:52.25,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,再见.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.96,0:41:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.43,0:41:54.99,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 祝你好运.\N- 你也是.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.59,0:41:55.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Good luck.\N- Good luck to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.34,0:42:15.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你能递一下豌豆吗, 唐娜?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.51,0:42:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you pass the peas, Donna?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.03,0:42:17.77,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.18,0:42:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.95,0:42:20.03,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 妈, 能问你点事吗?\N- 当然.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.12,0:42:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Mom, could l ask you something?\N- Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.21,0:42:22.47,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎么认识本杰明·荷恩的?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.38,0:42:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know Benjamin Horne?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.16,0:42:24.82,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,艾琳, 我告诉过唐娜了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.32,0:42:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eileen, l told Donna
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.99,0:42:28.82,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,就是你在进行的那个\N救治蓝色行星的慈善活动.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.16,0:42:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,about the Heal the Planet benefit\Nyou're working on.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.99,0:42:30.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,救治蓝色行星?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.16,0:42:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heal the Planet?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.82,0:42:33.08,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我看到他来这儿了.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.96,0:42:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l saw him at the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.25,0:42:35.38,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,然后，你昨天开车去见他?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.40,0:42:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You drove to see him yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.99,0:42:40.73,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊, 他说他会贡献一点时间\N和我们一起搞活动.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.17,0:42:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, he's offered to give us\Nsome time.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.03,0:42:44.34,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道他有善心\N去做几个本地的慈善活动.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.17,0:42:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l know he favors\Nseveral local charities.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.51,0:42:45.86,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那, 就一定是它了.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.68,0:42:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that must have been it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.03,0:42:49.29,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,一定是其中一个慈善会\N给妈妈送的玫瑰花\N.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.21,0:42:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One of the local charities\Nmust have sent Mom's roses.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.47,0:42:53.47,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你能递一下豌豆吗, 唐娜?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.62,0:42:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you pass the peas, Donna?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.68,0:42:56.90,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不过我觉得玫瑰真的很浪漫,\N你说呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.85,0:42:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l think roses are really romantic,\Ndon't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.08,0:43:00.34,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,唐娜, 递豌豆给你妈妈.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.26,0:43:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Donna, pass your mother the peas.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.21,0:43:09.51,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,在学校过的怎样?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.37,0:43:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's school going?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.21,0:43:11.77,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好极了.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.37,0:43:11.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.99,0:43:16.73,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,所有的女生都在为双峰小姐\N兴奋不已.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.17,0:43:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the girls are real excited\Nabout Miss Twin Peaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.86,0:43:19.77,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,优良传统.\N我参与选美工作好多年了.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.04,0:43:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine tradition.\Nl worked with the pageant for years.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.38,0:43:21.51,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我参加了.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.54,0:43:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l entered.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.03,0:43:24.68,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,真的?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.18,0:43:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.64,0:43:27.73,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你以前好像\N不是特别感兴趣.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.78,0:43:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You never seemed\Nvery interested before.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.21,0:43:29.38,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯, 我才想到的
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.39,0:43:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, l guess l just figured
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.55,0:43:32.64,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以用那笔奖学金\N出国留学.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.72,0:43:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l could use the scholarship money\Nto study overseas.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.81,0:44:08.51,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们觉得\N那可能是个炸弹.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.99,0:44:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We thought at first\Nit might be a bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.68,0:44:12.81,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们没有拆弹小组,\N所以安迪带了金属探测器.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.83,0:44:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't exactly have a bomb squad,\Nso Andy brought his metal detector.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.03,0:44:16.07,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是个炸弹, 却没有探出金属成分\N也没有嘀嗒声.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.20,0:44:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lf it is a bomb, it's not metallic\Nand there's no ticking sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.12,0:44:23.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哈里, 曾经有过一段时间\N我能以高度清晰的思维,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.27,0:44:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harry, there was a time\Nwhen l could comprehend,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.29,0:44:26.94,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,去完全理解,\N云顿·厄尔扭曲的逻辑.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.47,0:44:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with a high degree of clarity,\NWindom Earle's twisted logic.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.12,0:44:30.81,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但他最近的行动\N让我完全不知所措.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.28,0:44:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But his actions of late\Nhave left me completely bewildered.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.99,0:44:34.07,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他正改变棋盘\N上的格局.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.15,0:44:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is changing the pattern\Nof the game board.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.25,0:44:38.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,任何能推理他下一步行动的\N希望已经破灭了.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.42,0:44:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Any hope of deducing his next move\Nhas evaporated.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.29,0:44:40.64,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,安迪, 能麻烦你\N指挥大家
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.46,0:44:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Andy, would you please\Ndirect everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.81,0:44:43.51,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,躲到巡逻警车后吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.99,0:44:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,well behind the police cruiser?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.42,0:44:46.94,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哈里. 请大家往后站.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.60,0:44:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harry, please stand back.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.12,0:44:48.86,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,可能有塑料炸药\N在里面--
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.26,0:44:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There could be plastic explosives\Nin there--
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.07,0:44:51.16,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,库珀大家要大家\N躲到巡逻车后.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.23,0:44:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agent Cooper wants everyone back\Nbehind the cruiser.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.34,0:44:53.16,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,--化学物,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.50,0:44:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--chemicals,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.34,0:44:55.99,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不敢想像\N还会有什么鬼东西.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.50,0:44:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and whatever else\Nhell could imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.77,0:44:58.73,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我最大的恐惧?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.94,0:44:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My greatest fear?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.51,0:45:03.77,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,就是云顿·厄尔\N不再按逻辑出牌.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.68,0:45:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Windom Earle\Nmerely condescends to logic.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.90,0:45:10.16,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那留给我们的任务就艰巨了，要如何解释\N一个疯子那种可怕的反覆无常.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.05,0:45:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leaving us the task of unraveling\Nan insane man's terrifying caprice.
